{
  "texts": [
    "IntroductionThe timely availability of healthcare services is a fundamental requirement for every individual.",
    "A country's healthcare system is a crucial measure of its developmental progress [1][2][3].",
    "In this aspect, eHealth is highly beneficial asit offers healthcare to everyone, wherever.",
    "EHealth exemplifies technological advancements in expanding healthcare locally, nationally, and globally via the use of cutting-edge technologies (CET).",
    "It enables individuals who are unable to visit the clinic to access health services through continuous monitoring of vital signs using wearable or implantable IoT (Internet-of-Things) sensors, particularly for chronic and elderly patients."
  ]
}